<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=0.5">
    <title>Bienvenue sur MGC</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #1A3E3C;
            color: #FFFDE0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Bienvenue sur MGC</h1>
    <p>Nous sommes ravis de vous accueillir.</p>
</body>
</html>
